pes\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1843, \"end\": 1850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bayonne\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.795678761157724e-19, \"text\": \"Bayonne\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bayonne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bayonne\"}, {\"begin\": 1970, \"end\": 1975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.146364808413199e-36, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2055, \"end\": 2061, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seelow\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seelow\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seelow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seelow\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just hours before winning thegold medal in the women's 66kg Olympic boxing tournamentagainst China's Yang Liu on Friday, August 9, Algerian boxer Imane Khelif began a different battle in the courts.\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2238, \"end\": 2243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999765212478984, \"rank\": 2.3083921340518546e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 2246, \"end\": 2254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\", \"score\": 0.9999966834675861, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yang Liu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\"}, {\"begin\": 2276, \"end\": 2284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9993578012045157, \"rank\": 0.0006426114800897444, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 2291, \"end\": 2303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having been the victim, for more than a week, of a virulent smear campaign concerning her gender identity, the boxer filed a complaint against X with the Paris correctional court's, national center for combating online hate.\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2568, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2498, \"end\": 2503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.146364808413199e-36, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The complaint, whichLe Mondehad the opportunity to see, centers around online \\\"moral harassment.\\\"\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2667, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her victory resulting from the withdrawal in the quarter-finals of her opponent, Italian boxer Angela Carini, on August 1, triggered a flood of hate messages around the world across social media: She was described as a \\\"transgender\\\" person deliberately competing in the wrong category, and even a \\\"man\\\" guilty of \\\"violence against women.\\\"\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 3006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2749, \"end\": 2756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.786305017645943, \"rank\": 0.2710426670911526, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resour